These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, architect, photographer, police-officer
1. the police-officer is on the left or right of the coach##3
2. the coach is somewhere to the right of the police-officer##5
3. the architect is not to the left of the photographer##8
4. the architect is on the left of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |     2      |   3   |   4    |
| Job   | photographer | architect | police-officer | coach |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, coffee, juice
1. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking coffee##2
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |  2   |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | coffee | hot-chocolate | juice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-3::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, grapefruit, raspberry, mango
1. the person eating raspberry is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapefruit##5
2. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating mango##1
3. the person eating grapefruit is not to the left of the person eating mango##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |   2   |   3    |   4    |
| Food   | tomato | mango | grapefruit | raspberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, gardening, card-games, singing
1. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's hobby is gardening##7
2. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |      2      |       3       |   4    |
| Hobby   | gardening | singing | card-games | traveling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-5::.
