3. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##5
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |       3       |    4     |
| Sport   | skiing | badminton | rugby | soccer |

