2. the person eating banana is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating banana is not to the left of the person eating garlic##8
4. the person eating banana is the person eating banana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |     3     |   4   |
| Food   | apple | garlic | banana | onion |

